title: Lunchbox Thinks He’s Top 25 Most Famous People In Nashville + TWO Hit Wonder Game + Bobby Asks If You’d Eat these Crazy State Fair Foods
itunes:title: Lunchbox Thinks He’s Top 25 Most Famous People In Nashville + TWO Hit Wonder Game + Bobby Asks If You’d Eat these Crazy State Fair Foods
description:
Lunchbox did some great investigative reporting and talked to Starbucks baristas to find out if they get annoyed about crazy complex orders from customers. We play a game to see if you can identify the TWO hit wonder artists. Bobby reads a list of crazy new state fair foods and if we’d be down to eat them. Bobby also reads an email from a listener who is struggling with listening to her daughter as she practices the violin and needs advice on what to do.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
